| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1035 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ce156cfb-5041-5bb5-81f5-56c318ddacf5"
